But he said the police officers involved should refrain from
moving around heavily armed and in full combat gear.
</P>
<P>
The police officers should also immediately return all
vehicles they have seized, he added.
</P>
<P>
Mosakeng also called on other policemen who joined the mutiny
to return to their posts without delay.
</P>
<P>
The warning comes after last Thursday's seizure of the police
headquarters in Maseru by the mutinous officers.
</P>
<P>
The rebellious policemen dismissed six senior officers,
including the commissioner of police who was at the time out of
the country.
</P>
<P>
The renegade policemen have been resisting arrest for the 1995
murders of three fellow policemen who allegedly demanded amnesty.
