gainers of the day as it rose one dollar to finish at 19.4
Singapore dollars. The Singapore Press Holdings (SPH) Foreign
increased 90 cents to close at 29 Singapore dollars, while UMW
picked up 70 cents to end at 7.8 Singapore dollars.
</P>
