spot on the losers' list as each of them declined 40 cents to end
at 13.1 Singapore dollars and 10.7 US dollars respectively.
Gentings fell 25 cents to finish at 9.7 dollars, while Khong Guan
was 24 cents lower at 4.56 Singapore dollars.  
