yesterday called on the state-owned South African Airways to
speed up partial privatization.
</P>
<P>
-- Negotiators from South Africa and the European Union (EU)
is due to resume negotiations today in a bid to remove hurdles on
SA's qualified accession to the Lome Convention, a senior EU
official confirmed yesterday.
</P>
<P>
