<HEADLINE> Sampras Beats Radulescu in First Round </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, February 11 (Xinhua) -- Pete Sampras dispatched
Alex Radulescu of Germany 7-6 (7-3) 6-3 in the first round of the
$303,000 Sybase Open tennis tournament in San Jose, the United
States, on Tuesday.
</P>
