humiliated Ryan Wolters 6-0, 6-1 in just 49 minutes.
</P>
<P>
Only two singles matches were played in San Jose, because seven
players who will take part in eight scheduled first-round singles
matches on Wednesday competed for their respective countries in
the Davis Cup last weekend and had to fly long distances to reach
San Jose. 
