<HEADLINE> Earthquake Hits Jiashi County in Xinjiang </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
URUMQI, February 12 (Xinhua) -- An earthquake measuring 5.3 on
the Richter Scale jolted Jiashi county in northwest China's
Xinjiang Uygur Autonomous Region at 4:20 a.m. today.
</P>
