Defense Ministry officials on a possible deal to provide SU-27
fighters to Vietnam, the Interfax News Agency reported today.
</P>
<P>
The Rosvooruzheniye State Company, Russia's largest arms export
company and the Irkutsk Aircraft Manufacturing Company are now
finalising talks with the Vietnamese side, Interfax quoted company
officials as saying Today.
</P>
<P>
