Interfax said.
</P>
<P>
A top manager of the Irkutsk Aircraft Manufacturing Company
said the company was ready to hand over the first of 40 S-30MK
multi-purpose fighters to India according to a deal the two sides
reached late last year. India agreed to buy 40 S-30MK fighters at
the cost of 1.8 billion U.S. dollars from Russia. 
